Package org.eclipse.papyrus.designer.ucm.core.menu

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    EnhancedPopupMenu
    A specialized PopupMenu that supports the insertion of (1) separators into the menu.
    EnhancedPopupMenu.Disabled
    In a similar fashion to the PopupMenu.CascadingMenu, an object that can be added to the menu in order to create a separator, which is not an actionable item.
    EnhancedPopupMenu.Separator
    In a similar fashion to the PopupMenu.CascadingMenu, an object that can be added to the menu in order to create a separator, which is not an actionable item.
    EnhancedPopupMenu.SubSelect
    In a similar fashion to the PopupMenu.CascadingMenu, an object that will imply a sub-selection in a new box
    MenuHelper
    Simplify the creation of an enhanced popup menu
